{"tid":771533,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"即日起持特區護照遊泰國　歸類為支那人　只能使用支那特別通道","createTime":"2018-08-08T04:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T12:51:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aca4708527baeb032bfa92961f6e4d1bdef0767e","tid":771533,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/feature_17814045855b694d29c5688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Ffeature_17814045855b694d29c5688.jpg&h=cb8ea4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【泰國機場】早前泰國布吉島發生船難，造成至少42人死亡，當中大部分是中國旅客。中國大陸遊客一向是泰國旅遊業的大客，為了挽回中國旅客的信心，5個泰國機場增設了中國遊客入境的專屬通道，方便他們。有網民剛從曼谷回來，分享過關經驗，指持有香港特區護照同樣須排中國遊客專屬通道。<br />\n<br />\n由8月3日起，位於曼谷的蘇萬那普國際機場、廊曼國際機場，和清邁、合艾和布吉等5個有中國直航的泰國機場，增設了中國遊客的專屬VIP入境通道。以蘇萬那普國際機場為例，一共開設了17個專屬通道，為數不少。<br />\n<br />\n泰國此舉原意是挽回中國遊客對泰國的信心，並有分流作用。<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不過有網民指這是另類種族隔離，讓中國旅客自己人打自己人，即使排隊打尖，也只是他們之間的事，不怕影響其他地方的旅客。</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/d0a732bfgy1ftwtk03f16j20rt0kuq6t_2217843545b692ccaecd91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fd0a732bfgy1ftwtk03f16j20rt0kuq6t_2217843545b692ccaecd91.jpg&h=7c498e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有一定分流作用，但因為中國旅客實在太多，支那通道有時比其他通道還要多人，機場職員也不得不將中國旅客安排到其他通道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/-2018-08-07-13.17.11_9623197595b692cb7d4a2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F-2018-08-07-13.17.11_9623197595b692cb7d4a2e.png&h=7f5c6e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有香港網民剛從曼谷回來，表示持有香港特區護照也被歸納為中國旅客，須要排支那特別通道過境。對大家而言，未知是好消息還是壞消息呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/-2018-08-07-13.12.18_10275638765b692c24b104a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F-2018-08-07-13.12.18_10275638765b692c24b104a.png&h=e7079a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/-2018-08-07-13.17.34_18561561605b692c45efa2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F-2018-08-07-13.17.34_18561561605b692c45efa2c.png&h=7104cf58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"191a74e4bda1846a036ac56d1046072404b9702b","tid":771533,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"VIP=Very Inconvrnient People"}]}